#| "\n"
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Map Tile Pool:} Each player takes 1 random Far (II-III) Map Tile.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\textbf{Набор фрагментов карты:} Каждый игрок берёт 1 случайный ближний (IV--V) фрагмент карты и 1 дальний (II--III) фрагмент карты. Эти фрагменты не должны содержать Обелисков.\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols*
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:37 coops/the_ambushed_accord.tex:40
#: clash/astral_run.tex:34
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Map Setup}}\n"
"Take the following Map Tiles ($P$ stands for the number of players) and arrange them as shown in the Scenario map layout:\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Возьмите следующие фрагменты карты и расположите по схеме карты сценария:\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:43
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "\\begin{itemize}\n"
#| "  \\item 2 × Starting (I) Map Tile\n"
#| "  \\item 4 × Far (II--III) Map Tile\n"
#| "  \\item 4 × Near (IV--V) Map Tile with the Obelisk Field\n"
#| "\\end{itemize}\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item $P$ × Starting (I) Map Tiles\n"
"  \\item 2$P$ × Near (IV–V) Map Tiles\n"
"  \\item 1 × Center (VI–VII) Map Tile with Dragon Utopia\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item 2 × Стартовый (I) фрагмент карты\n"
"  \\item 4 × Дальний  (II--III) фрагмент карты\n"
"  \\item 4 × Ближний (IV--V) фрагмент карты с полем Обелиска\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:46
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
#| msgid ""
#| "\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Victory Conditions}}\n"
#| "\n"
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Victory Conditions}}\n"
"Defeat the wandering dragons and flag the Dragon Utopia.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Условия победы}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:57
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Timed Events}}\n"
"\\textbf{\\nth{4} Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Remove all Black Cubes from all Water Wheels and Windmills on the map.\n"
"  \\item The wandering dragons gain $+1$ to the movement dice roll this Round (see Additional Rules below).\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\textbf{\\nth{8} Round:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item Repeat events of the \\nth{4} Round.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\subsection*{\\MakeUppercase{Additional Rules}}\n"
"Randomly draw the following Neutral dragon Unit Cards into two \\textbf{Dragon Decks}: Dragon Utopia (DU) and wandering dragons (WD):\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:82
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\textbf{Easy:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item DU: 2 × \\svg{azure}\n"
"  \\item WD: 2 × \\svg{golden} (+1 \\svg{golden} if 3 players)\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\textbf{Normal:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item DU: 2 × \\svg{azure}, 1 × \\svg{golden}\n"
"  \\item WD: 1 × \\svg{azure}, 1 × \\svg{golden} (+1 \\svg{golden} if 3 players)\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\textbf{Hard:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item DU: 3 × \\svg{azure}\n"
"  \\item WD: 1 × \\svg{azure}, 2 × \\svg{golden} (+1 \\svg{golden} if 3 players)\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\textbf{Impossible:}\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item DU: 3 × \\svg{azure}, 1 × \\svg{golden}\n"
"  \\item WD: 2 × \\svg{azure}, 1 × \\svg{golden} (+1 \\svg{golden} if 3 players)\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: coops/wandering_dragons.tex:102
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"  \\item The WD start at the center of the undiscovered Center Map Tile and are marked with a \\svg{morale_negative} token.\n"
"  \\item The WD \\textbf{do not discover} Map Tiles they move through.\n"
"  \\item The WD move at the end of every Round. Roll 2 Attack Dice and add 1 to the result. On a result of:\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{1 or more}, the WD move that amount of Fields toward the player asset (Hero, Town, or Settlement) that is closest to them.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{0}, the WD stay in place.\n"
"    \\item \\textbf{--1}, the WD move one Field toward the DU.\n"
"  \\end {itemize}\n"
"  \\columnbreak\n"
"  \\item If two or more player assets are equidistant, the WD prioritize 1)~Heroes, 2)~Towns and 3)~Settlements.\n"
"    If this does not resolve which direction the WD should move, roll a die to determine the target.\n"
"  \\item The WD attack if they reach a Field with a Hero, a Town, or a Settlement with a Hero.\n"
"    In this case, the battle is fought until the end without a chance for retreat.\n"
"    If the WD reach a Settlement without a Hero in it, remove the Faction Cube from it.\n"
"  \\item The WD may move through Blocked Fields but cannot end their movement on one.\n"
"  \\item The player who defeats the WD gains \\svg{morale_positive}.\n"
"  \\item \\textbf{Obelisk:} Roll \\svg{treasure} and \\svg{resource} and resolve both.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""

